   <H1>[IPT] IPT v2.0 is ready</H1>
    <B>Oliver Meyn (GBIF)</B> 
    <A HREF="mailto:ipt%40lists.gbif.org?Subject=Re:%20%5BIPT%5D%20IPT%20v2.0%20is%20ready&In-Reply-To=%3C3A2A263A-6C6C-4DED-954C-1DC4A5CEC7B3%40gbif.org%3E"
